<div style="float: left; width: 40%;">
<h2>Build Your Town</h2>
<p>With nothing but their wits and strength, your hardy band of hearthlings will carve a place in the wilderness. Watch a clearing become a camp, and then a town&#8230; and soon, a thriving outpost of civilization! There are no limits on what you can build&#8230; what your settlers can imagine, they can create.
</p></div>
<div style="float: left; width: 60%"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-2067" src="http://stonehearth.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/build-1024x580.png" alt="build" width="640" height="363" srcset="https://www.stonehearth.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/build-1024x580.png 1024w, https://www.stonehearth.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/build-300x170.png 300w, https://www.stonehearth.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/build.png 1038w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></div>
<div style="clear:both;" />
